listitem.para:
Susan Williams reported success in installing DB2 Version 7.1 on Debian using the following script as root:
Installation script for DB2 Version 7.1 on Debian
#!/bin/bash cd / for f in /mnt/cdrom1/db2/*rpm do alien -d -i -c $f done

For further information on installing DB2 on Linux distributions which use the dpkg
package manager, see Tiago Antao's page,
Agnostic DB2 V7.1 for GNU/Linux.
